Saudi Second-Quarter Wholesale Index Rises 4.8% From Year Ago

-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 
2011-08-10T11:28:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-10/saudi-second-quarter-wholesale-index-rises-4-8-from-year-ago.html
Saudi Arabia ’s wholesale price index
increased 4.8 percent in the second quarter from the same period
a year earlier, the  Central Department of Statistics and
Information  said in a quarterly report on its website today.  The index rose 1.7 percent in the second quarter from the
first three months of this year, according to the agency’s data.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
 mharoutunian@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
